/************
This file is an Umple translation of a model
of OCCAM version 0.1 found at the following URL
https://github.com/atlanmod/atlantic-zoo/blob/main/AtlantEcore/OCCAM.ecore

date: 2006/07/25

Description: This metamodel describes OCCAM. OCCAM is a parallel processing language designed by a team at INMOS in conjunction with the design of the transputer processor, and based on T. Hoare s ideas of CSP.

Title: Occam

See: http://www.wotug.org/occam/

Authors: Youssef SROUR (Srour.youssef_NOSPAM <AT> gmail.com)
